00:28:50.070 --> 00:28:53.280
You explain to him that there are several alternatives,

654
00:28:53.280 --> 00:28:54.753
but according to the USPSTF,

655
00:28:55.710 --> 00:28:58.110
recommendations regarding the optimal screening

656
00:28:58.110 --> 00:29:01.140
intervals will vary by test.

657
00:29:01.140 --> 00:29:02.883
