00:30:12.990 --> 00:30:15.960
Here's why they don't worry about the test chosen

686
00:30:15.960 --> 00:30:17.880
because the number of lives saved

687
00:30:17.880 --> 00:30:21.573
just based on screening is basically the same.

688
00:30:22.800 --> 00:30:24.060
Basically the same.

