00:30:52.670 --> 00:30:55.440
their recall is like the general population,

701
00:30:55.440 --> 00:30:59.880
10 years if I'm choosing colonoscopy.

702
00:30:59.880 --> 00:31:01.350
The single first degree relative

703
00:31:01.350 --> 00:31:03.210
with CRC or an advanced adenoma

704
00:31:03.210 --> 00:31:05.580
