706
00:31:07.860 --> 00:31:10.560
than the initial or sentinel event.

707
00:31:10.560 --> 00:31:13.260
Their interval would be five years.

708
00:31:13.260 --> 00:31:15.030
Two first degree relatives

709
00:31:15.030 --> 00:31:18.270
or an advanced adenoma diagnosed at any age.

710
00:31:18.270 --> 00:31:21.600
Again, the interval of screening is five years.

711
00:31:21.600 --> 00:31:23.460
The AGA and their choosing wisely.

712
00:31:23.460 --> 00:31:25.650
Do not repeat colorectal cancer screening

713
00:31:25.650 --> 00:31:28.110
by any method for 10 years

714
00:31:28.110 --> 00:31:29.722
after a high quality colonoscopy

715
00:31:29.722 --> 00:31:32.370
that does not detect neoplasia.

716
00:31:32.370 --> 00:31:33.810
I had a patient about two years ago.

