00:32:05.160 --> 00:32:07.020
It's not indicated for prostate cancer.

731
00:32:07.020 --> 00:32:09.420
Never heard from them again either.

732
00:32:09.420 --> 00:32:10.653
Okay, our last question.

733
00:32:11.963 --> 00:32:13.380
One week after a complete

734
00:32:13.380 --> 00:32:15.330
and adequate baseline screening colonoscopy,

735
00:32:15.330 --> 00:32:17.460
a 51-year-old female with no history

